+  background rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)
+  border none
+  height 100%
+  cursor pointer
+  border-radius 99rem
+  display grid
+  place-items center
+  aspect-ratio 1
+  opacity 1
+  transition all 300ms
+  font-size 1rem
+  user-select none
+
+.btn:hover
+  color grey
+
+.btn--vr
+  padding 0 2rem
+  aspect-ratio inherit
+
+.btn--xr
+  position fixed
+  top 50%
+  left 50%
+  transform translate(-50%, -50%)
+  padding 2rem 4rem
+  border-radius 99rem
+  display grid
+  place-items center
+  font-size 1.5rem
+  background #000
+  border none
+  z-index 1000
+
+.btn--vr:hover, .svg
+  color white
+
+.ui-wrap, .init-ui
+  position absolute
+  inset 0
+  will-change transform
+
+.init-ui
+  z-index 30
+  pointer-events none
+  // opacity 0
+
+.ui-wrap
+  z-index 40
+  opacity 0
+  pointer-events none
+
+.ui__img
+  width 100%
+  position absolute
+
+.ui__img--top
+  top 0
+
+.ui__img--bottom
+  bottom 0
+
+.ui__btns
+  position absolute
+  top 2rem
+  right 4rem
+  display flex
+  height 4.5rem
+  gap 1rem
+  z-index 50
+  pointer-events auto
+
+$pad = 3vw
+
+.top-ui, .bottom-ui
+  position absolute

+  width calc(100vw - %s * 2) % $pad
+  left 5vw
+  display flex
+  height 4.5rem

+  justify-content space-between
+
+.top-ui
+  top $pad
+
+.bottom-ui
+  bottom $pad
+
+.ui__nav
+  display flex
+  gap 1rem
+
+.title
+  position absolute
+  height 3rem
+  left 50%
+  translate -50%
+

+  height 4rem
